N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1211.50 - Weapons of war employing atomic fission or forbidden explosives

State Regulations

No vehicle shall enter either a tunnel, the George

Washington Bridge Lower Level or George Washington Bridge Expressway if its
load includes any weapon of war employing atomic fission or radioactive force, or any forbidden explosives as defined by D.O.T. regulations. Notes
